Field.Name: GOOD

Field.Name: BAD_BY_DEVICE
Field.Description: For ConsumerStatus: The IO device has locally detected problems to convey data. For ProviderStatus: The content of the submodule’s IO data object is invalid. The condition was detected by the device.
